= What is Xuggle-Utils ? =

Xuggle-Utils is a collection of utility classes that Xuggle
has decided to open-source.  We use these classes extensively
in our closed-source code.

Examples of classes found here are a Decoupled Event Dispatching
model (similar to ActionScript's EventDispatcher model), and
a State Machine implementation.

= Where can I find documentation? =
Visit http://www.xuggle.com/xuggler/doc

or build the documentaiton yourself:
  ant doc
and then open up
  doc/java/api/index.html (the Java docs).

= Where can I find out more? =
Visit:
http://www.xuggle.com/xuggler

